(5, 'privacy', '{\"en\": \"Privacy Policy\", \"ru\": \"–ü–æ–ª–∏—Ç–∏–∫–∞ –∫–æ–Ω—Ñ–∏–¥–µ–Ω—Ü–∏–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ—Å—Ç–∏\"}', 'privacy-policy', 1, '{\"en\": {\"text\": \"<p>This regulation defines rules of privacy protection for kratomhelper.com. This a regulation for the flow of information accumulated on the website.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The following issues are about</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&mdash; Personally identifiable information that is stored on via the website. The way it is operated with and sharing restrictions.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&mdash; Operating options for customers</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&mdash; The due diligence for avoiding misusing of private information</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&mdash; The way of correcting and improving any inaccuracies or disinformation</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Information Collection, Use, and Sharing</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The website owners possess the information stored on it. Only the owner or his envoys have access to the data that customers voluntarily transfer to the website.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>This data is used only to make the service more client-oriented and respond to all the requests that our customers send us. It can&rsquo;t be shared, sold, or rented to any third party outside the organization except the cases to fulfill the obligations undertaken under a contract with customers appear. That can be a necessity to arrange shipping or any similar case.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Orders</strong></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You submit the information via a special order form. To purchase any product on the website you are to fulfill the form and mention contacts (name and delivery address). This is necessary for billing and filling orders tickets. If there is any trouble with processing an order, our managers contact you.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We may also use contact information to promote our new items and services, or changes in the Private Policy.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>There is an option to refuse to get our promoting email.</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>At the same time, our customers can 