nts: the more you buy, the cheaper the kratom cost per 1 gram is</p>\", \"compensation_c_3\": \"<p>Each you feedback brings you $1-2 on your personal account. You may use this money for any order in our e-shop. If your feedback includes a Facebook page link, you get $2, if not &ndash; just $1. If your feedback is a negative one, you get the money anyway. We are kindly asking you to write just honest feedbacks as far as they will be read by other visitors, who would like to be sure that your feedbacks are objective and honest.</p>\", \"compensation_t_1\": \"Compensation for orders\", \"compensation_t_2\": \"Volume discounts\", \"compensation_t_3\": \"Money for feedback\", \"compensation_mt_1\": \"COMPENSATION\", \"partner_program_info\": \"<p>We offer you to earn with us. We have a splendid referral program. You should not be registered as our Partner for this. Each registered user can generate a set of his/her own links. If a new customer registers and makes an order by following your link, you get 10% of this customer&rsquo;s order amount. If this customer creates his/her own link and invites another customer (who makes an order), you get 5% of the latter&rsquo;s customer&rsquo;s order amount. And so on up to the third degree. The order in the third degree brings you 2% of an order amount. To get the money, the order must have a &#39;sent&#39; status. It means that the order was paid and sent. If the customer decides to return the order, it will not be your concern (as far as we are ready for such expenses). It should be noted that the money is real (not bonus), so you are able to get this money out any way you prefer. Your referral network will be seen in your personal cabinet, so you will have the possibility to check the orders of the people from your network yourself. Let&rsquo;s earn together! Bring your friends to us!</p>\"}, \"ru\": {\"htw_info\": \"<p>–ï—Å–ª–∏ –Ω–æ–≤—ã–π –∫–ª–∏–µ–Ω—Ç —Ä–∞–∑–º–µ—â–∞–µ—Ç –∑–∞–∫–∞–∑ –ø–æ –≤–∞—à–µ–π —Å—Å—ã–ª–∫–µ –±–µ–∑ —Ä–µ–≥–∏